WEBVTT

01:36.979 --> 01:40.930
[The Best Thing]

01:41.410 --> 01:45.680
[Episode 7: Osmanthus is sweet and sour in taste and warm in nature. It warms the middle, dispels cold, harmonizes the stomach, and regulates qi.]

01:53.640 --> 01:54.520
Hello, Mom.

01:55.229 --> 01:55.870
Ms. Shen.

01:56.920 --> 01:58.590
Don't make any plans for this weekend, okay?

01:59.070 --> 01:59.870
Why?

02:00.470 --> 02:01.830
I'll tell you when you get home tonight.

02:02.690 --> 02:05.690
You're already on the phone, so just say it now.

02:06.640 --> 02:07.640
I'll tell you tonight.

02:08.310 --> 02:09.910
I'm afraid you might make plans

02:09.910 --> 02:11.009
with Xiangya and Lin again,

02:11.030 --> 02:12.540
so I'm telling you in advance.

02:12.570 --> 02:13.850
No plans for this weekend.

02:13.870 --> 02:14.520
I'm hanging up now.

02:19.800 --> 02:20.870
No plans for this weekend.

02:21.550 --> 02:22.590
Then I'll make some tomorrow.

02:28.750 --> 02:30.060
I made it according to your recipe.

02:30.630 --> 02:31.680
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

02:31.970 --> 02:32.690
I'm not going.

02:32.710 --> 02:33.700
Why not?

02:33.810 --> 02:34.880
That guy

02:34.980 --> 02:35.790
looks good.

02:35.810 --> 02:36.560
He's also tall

02:36.560 --> 02:37.670
and well-educated.

02:37.960 --> 02:38.840
He was recommended

02:38.840 --> 02:39.630
by Mr. Shen's classmate from Normal University, right?

02:39.630 --> 02:40.400
Yes.

02:40.400 --> 02:41.630
So at least we know his background.

02:42.590 --> 02:44.470
I don't care. I'm not going.

02:44.470 --> 02:45.750
Haven't you heard what people say?

02:45.780 --> 02:48.460
The ones introduced by family and friends are all leftovers.

02:48.800 --> 02:50.470
Ms. Shen, you've got it backward.

02:50.470 --> 02:52.400
You're not being set up.

02:52.400 --> 02:54.430
The two of us have chosen someone for you.

02:54.430 --> 02:55.840
The advantage is on our side.

02:55.840 --> 02:56.360
Yes.

02:56.360 --> 02:57.960
We've gone through several rounds of screening.

02:57.960 --> 02:59.280
These are the ones left.

02:59.280 --> 02:59.910
I don't care.

02:59.910 --> 03:00.910
I'm not going.

03:00.910 --> 03:02.190
Isn't the key point here

03:02.190 --> 03:03.960
whether I want to or not?

03:03.960 --> 03:05.000
I don't want to.

03:05.000 --> 03:06.080
It's already September.

03:06.080 --> 03:07.630
I'm about to study abroad.

03:07.630 --> 03:08.750
He can wait for you.

03:08.960 --> 03:10.560
Did you even ask if he's willing to wait?

03:10.630 --> 03:12.000
Fine, so I should fall in love again,

03:12.000 --> 03:12.840
break up again,

03:12.840 --> 03:14.430
and then be heartbroken once more?

03:14.910 --> 03:15.870
It's not that serious.

03:15.870 --> 03:17.079
You're overthinking it.

03:17.079 --> 03:19.520
Yeah. Besides, he's a TCM physician.

03:19.520 --> 03:20.560
A TCM physician.

03:20.950 --> 03:21.820
That profession

03:21.840 --> 03:22.910
has so many perks.

03:22.910 --> 03:24.000
Exactly.

03:24.000 --> 03:25.400
A guy studying TCM…

03:25.400 --> 03:26.680
He understands traditional culture.

03:26.680 --> 03:28.800
He's reserved and calm.

03:28.800 --> 03:29.280
That's right.

03:29.280 --> 03:29.680
Good.

03:30.079 --> 03:31.030
Speaking of TCM,

03:31.030 --> 03:32.630
I think this medicinal dish Dad made

03:32.630 --> 03:33.930
is quite good.

03:34.040 --> 03:35.760
It's perfect for autumn nourishment.

03:36.200 --> 03:37.110
What a coincidence.

03:37.110 --> 03:38.640
Look at her now.

03:38.640 --> 03:39.550
She knows a lot about TCM.

03:39.550 --> 03:40.270
Yeah, yeah.

03:40.270 --> 03:42.240
You've seen TCM physicians a few times,

03:42.240 --> 03:43.360
and now you're interested in TCM, huh?

03:43.360 --> 03:44.670
I'm not interested.

03:44.670 --> 03:45.710
I just drank too many decoctions.

03:45.710 --> 03:46.360
It doesn't matter.

03:46.920 --> 03:47.640
The key is—

03:47.640 --> 03:49.550
you two have something in common.

03:49.550 --> 03:51.150
How is that something in common?

03:51.150 --> 03:52.200
Come on, Ms. Shen.

03:52.800 --> 03:53.640
Just go meet him.

03:55.390 --> 03:56.800
Let him take your pulse.

03:57.150 --> 03:58.710
Have a check-up.

03:58.710 --> 04:00.320
You two can have a chat.

04:00.870 --> 04:03.030
He'll think I have issues.

04:03.080 --> 04:04.360
You don't have any major issues.

04:04.360 --> 04:05.520
Just insomnia.

04:05.520 --> 04:06.870
Insomnia is still an issue.

04:06.870 --> 04:07.640
It's not a real illness.

04:07.640 --> 04:08.240
It is.

04:08.240 --> 04:08.640
Well...

04:08.640 --> 04:10.150
You two just eat.

04:10.680 --> 04:14.070
Are you going or not?

04:14.100 --> 04:14.810
No.

04:15.060 --> 04:15.710
Just go.

04:15.860 --> 04:16.339
No.

04:22.640 --> 04:23.590
I sent you the info

04:23.590 --> 04:25.150
on that TCM physician. Did you see it?

04:25.880 --> 04:26.560
Yeah, I saw it.

04:27.560 --> 04:28.270
Where are you going?

04:28.760 --> 04:29.440
I'm going for a follow-up visit.

04:30.080 --> 04:30.880
Perfect.

04:31.910 --> 04:33.760
While you're there, ask your physician

04:33.760 --> 04:35.470
if he knows the guy you'll meet tomorrow.

04:37.150 --> 04:38.520
That would be so awkward.

04:38.520 --> 04:39.440
I'd die of embarrassment.

04:39.440 --> 04:40.270
What's there to be embarrassed about?

04:40.270 --> 04:41.320
Make up an excuse.

04:41.760 --> 04:42.790
What kind of excuse?

04:42.790 --> 04:43.520
That's too hard.

04:43.520 --> 04:43.909
I won't do it.

04:44.150 --> 04:44.880
Just say

04:45.440 --> 04:46.150
this guy

04:46.150 --> 04:47.590
is my friend's son.

04:47.830 --> 04:48.980
If he knows him,

04:49.000 --> 04:50.970
ask about his character

04:51.000 --> 04:52.120
and personality;

04:52.120 --> 04:53.470
ask if he's filial

04:53.590 --> 04:54.909
and if he treats girls well.

04:55.460 --> 04:56.540
I won't do it.

04:56.640 --> 04:57.350
You have to.

04:57.350 --> 04:58.520
Why are you so shy?

04:58.720 --> 05:00.060
Just ask. I'll be waiting for your update.

05:07.590 --> 05:08.350
No way.

05:09.150 --> 05:10.150
Your washed shirt.

05:10.390 --> 05:11.630
Thanks for your help the other day.

05:12.010 --> 05:12.840
Thank you.

05:17.520 --> 05:18.790
Sorry…

05:19.830 --> 05:20.630
about that night.

05:21.710 --> 05:22.830
I didn't scare you, did I?

05:24.440 --> 05:25.440
It's okay.

05:25.880 --> 05:26.820
That's what friends are for.

05:27.150 --> 05:29.750
You were feeling down, and I comforted you.

05:31.880 --> 05:33.030
Thank you for your comfort.

05:36.810 --> 05:38.370
Come on, let me take your pulse.

05:39.150 --> 05:39.640
Okay.

05:47.270 --> 05:49.120
How have you been lately?

05:51.480 --> 05:52.600
Pretty good.

05:53.070 --> 05:53.830
Okay.

05:56.320 --> 05:57.270
Dr. He,

05:57.920 --> 05:59.920
how do you treat menopause?

06:00.330 --> 06:02.210
What? Did you have a fight with your mom?

06:02.440 --> 06:04.080
Not exactly a fight.

06:04.440 --> 06:07.560
Just a little disagreement.

06:07.990 --> 06:08.710
Disagreement?

06:09.270 --> 06:10.030
About studying abroad?

06:12.230 --> 06:13.320
You know,

06:13.320 --> 06:14.680
at our age,

06:14.680 --> 06:16.710
our family loves to nag.

06:17.080 --> 06:18.350
Especially my mom.

06:18.350 --> 06:19.830
She nags nonstop.

06:20.080 --> 06:21.230
At home, she keeps saying

06:21.230 --> 06:21.760
things like,

06:22.450 --> 06:23.910
"You're already 27.

06:23.910 --> 06:25.150
Aren't you anxious?"

06:25.520 --> 06:26.270
What's there to be anxious about?

06:26.270 --> 06:27.390
Why should I be anxious?

06:27.570 --> 06:29.280
And it's not just her.

06:29.300 --> 06:31.150
My dad nags me with her.

06:31.180 --> 06:33.940
It's like the two of them are doing a sketch.

06:34.990 --> 06:36.180
It's not about studying abroad,

06:36.790 --> 06:37.909
so it's about…

06:38.830 --> 06:39.760
marriage?

06:40.409 --> 06:41.210
Dr. He.

06:44.760 --> 06:45.470
Dr. He.

06:47.000 --> 06:47.830
Sorry.

06:47.830 --> 06:49.320
Was I talking too much?

06:49.610 --> 06:51.640
Guess I've been influenced by my parents.

06:51.909 --> 06:53.150
No, I was just checking your pulse.

06:53.520 --> 06:54.390
Give me your other hand.

06:54.659 --> 06:55.510
Okay.

07:02.150 --> 07:04.000
Is there an acupuncture technique

07:04.000 --> 07:05.390
that can make me

07:05.390 --> 07:07.320
instantly tune them out?

07:08.440 --> 07:09.200
Nope.

07:09.590 --> 07:10.790
I'm a physician, not a magician.

07:16.450 --> 07:17.120
Alright.

07:23.030 --> 07:24.080
Then let's

07:25.230 --> 07:26.030
do moxibustion?

07:27.230 --> 07:27.960
Moxibustion?

07:28.640 --> 07:29.270
Okay.

07:29.310 --> 07:30.430
I'll get things ready for you.

07:41.710 --> 07:42.860
This is the prescription.

07:43.350 --> 07:44.080
Pharmacy decoction.

07:44.080 --> 07:45.230
Come pick it up in four hours.

07:45.560 --> 07:46.320
Thanks a lot.

07:46.320 --> 07:46.909
See you.

08:06.320 --> 08:06.910
Here.

08:07.900 --> 08:09.290
Have some snacks.

08:13.910 --> 08:15.790
I just saw Shen Xifan.

08:17.640 --> 08:19.930
How are things between her and her boyfriend?

08:22.150 --> 08:24.030
They're probably thinking about marriage

08:24.440 --> 08:25.680
and will get married soon.

08:27.560 --> 08:28.830
That fast?

08:32.679 --> 08:34.440
You should just get over her.

08:37.320 --> 08:38.350
I never expected anything to begin with.

08:39.280 --> 08:40.559
I'm just her physician.

08:43.830 --> 08:46.710
Your tone doesn't sound as indifferent as you claim.

08:48.960 --> 08:49.590
What else

08:49.870 --> 08:50.710
am I supposed to do?

09:01.280 --> 09:03.280
But there's one thing I don't quite get.

09:04.230 --> 09:05.510
Her boyfriend doesn't seem

09:05.680 --> 09:07.000
to treat her very well.

09:07.150 --> 09:08.630
So why is she marrying him?

09:11.340 --> 09:12.630
Matters of the heart

09:12.630 --> 09:14.200
can't be forced.

09:18.080 --> 09:19.130
No matter how smart

09:19.420 --> 09:20.790
or outstanding someone is,

09:21.630 --> 09:23.610
they can still make foolish choices

09:23.870 --> 09:24.770
in love.

09:28.510 --> 09:29.440
That's true.

09:31.750 --> 09:32.830
For a while,

09:33.630 --> 09:35.470
she didn't mention her boyfriend at all.

09:35.790 --> 09:37.360
I almost forgot about him.

09:38.400 --> 09:39.320
I even started

09:39.940 --> 09:41.420
getting the wrong idea.

09:46.040 --> 09:47.440
At my age,

09:48.130 --> 09:49.440
I was still reading into things.

09:49.780 --> 09:51.110
I really should move on.

09:53.070 --> 09:54.590
You're a hopeless romantic, huh?

09:54.620 --> 09:55.980
That's tragic.

09:57.280 --> 09:58.400
Hey, old man,

09:58.590 --> 09:59.280
I'm your grandson.

09:59.280 --> 10:00.750
Can't you show me a little sympathy?

10:01.040 --> 10:02.200
Alright, I feel bad for you.

10:03.400 --> 10:04.870
But seriously,

10:05.190 --> 10:06.070
in the past,

10:06.100 --> 10:08.530
you were too focused on work and studies.

10:08.860 --> 10:09.980
So I

10:10.000 --> 10:12.760
never pushed you to go on blind dates.

10:13.480 --> 10:16.080
But now that you're thinking about it,

10:16.920 --> 10:19.990
maybe it's time to meet someone?

10:20.750 --> 10:23.870
There are plenty of outstanding female doctors

10:23.870 --> 10:26.230
and beautiful nurses in major hospitals.

10:26.470 --> 10:27.320
Here we go again.

10:28.080 --> 10:29.510
If you don't want someone from the same field,

10:29.900 --> 10:33.330
there are plenty of excellent women in other professions.

10:37.350 --> 10:38.320
"The Yellow Emperor's Inner Canon"

10:38.590 --> 10:39.560
says something about this

10:39.560 --> 10:41.560
in On Art of Health Cultivation in Ancient Times.

10:42.440 --> 10:42.920
"For a man

10:43.350 --> 10:44.200
at 24,

10:44.590 --> 10:46.110
his kidney energy is balanced,

10:46.990 --> 10:48.750
and his tendons and bones are strong,

10:49.280 --> 10:51.920
so wisdom teeth come in, and his body reaches its peak.

10:52.750 --> 10:55.750
At 32, tendons and bones are at their prime,

10:55.900 --> 10:57.540
and muscles are strong."

10:57.570 --> 10:59.740
That's exactly your current age.

11:00.230 --> 11:00.920
And after that…

11:00.920 --> 11:02.040
I know—

11:02.750 --> 11:05.080
"Liver energy weakens, and tendons lose their flexibility."

11:06.960 --> 11:08.070
Are you talking about me?

11:10.910 --> 11:11.940
No matter what,

11:12.270 --> 11:15.790
this is the natural law of human physical development.

11:16.160 --> 11:18.200
You can't go against it.

11:18.960 --> 11:22.510
Don't waste the prime years of your life.

11:23.920 --> 11:25.280
Alright, I got it.

11:25.990 --> 11:27.800
Don't worry about this.

11:27.990 --> 11:29.510
I'll handle it as I see fit.

11:33.440 --> 11:35.630
Every time we get to the key part,

11:35.630 --> 11:37.110
you brush me off.

11:38.470 --> 11:39.400
Have some tea.

11:39.400 --> 11:40.920
Stop worrying about my affairs.

11:47.190 --> 11:48.080
Hello.

11:48.270 --> 11:50.460
I have an appointment with the oncology department at 1 p.m.

11:50.620 --> 11:52.020
Can I go in now?

11:52.470 --> 11:54.040
It's not office hours yet.

11:54.070 --> 11:56.000
You can wait in the rest area for a while.

11:56.020 --> 11:56.960
Okay.

11:56.430 --> 11:58.090
[Guidance Station]

12:25.440 --> 12:27.200
Overall, the paper is fine,

12:27.680 --> 12:28.680
but for the section

12:28.680 --> 12:30.830
on post-mastectomy complications,

12:30.830 --> 12:32.920
you could add some clinical cases

12:32.920 --> 12:34.080
as supporting evidence.

12:34.080 --> 12:35.990
It would make the paper more convincing.

12:35.990 --> 12:36.870
Got it.

12:38.630 --> 12:39.510
Actually,

12:39.510 --> 12:40.590
if you want to publish your paper

12:40.590 --> 12:42.080
in a journal,

12:42.350 --> 12:44.080
you could ask my grandfather to be your advisor.

12:44.080 --> 12:45.040
He's more authoritative.

12:46.290 --> 12:48.530
I feel like my questions are too basic,

12:48.680 --> 12:50.560
so I'd feel awkward asking Professor Yu.

12:51.120 --> 12:52.520
I feel more comfortable…

12:55.480 --> 12:56.650
discussing them with you.

12:59.750 --> 13:01.920
My grandfather is quite kind to you all, isn't he?

13:02.590 --> 13:04.230
He loves it when students ask him questions.

13:04.230 --> 13:05.960
You can talk to him more when you have time.

13:08.320 --> 13:08.990
Okay.

13:14.200 --> 13:15.110
Well,

13:15.800 --> 13:16.660
Senior He,

13:17.630 --> 13:19.490
I keep coming to you with questions,

13:19.580 --> 13:21.150
and I feel a bit bad about it.

13:22.440 --> 13:23.860
Let me treat you to dinner tonight.

13:24.510 --> 13:25.030
No need.

13:25.680 --> 13:26.800
It's my duty to offer you guidance.

13:26.800 --> 13:27.990
This is part of my job.

13:34.210 --> 13:34.860
Look,

13:35.080 --> 13:36.080
this is exactly…

13:36.910 --> 13:37.670
Suye.

13:40.350 --> 13:42.510
I need to talk to you about something personal.

13:43.590 --> 13:45.190
Whenever you talk like that, it's never good news.

13:46.080 --> 13:48.160
It's definitely good news this time.

13:49.080 --> 13:49.990
Fang,

13:50.200 --> 13:51.200
could you…

13:53.530 --> 13:55.530
Take your paper back and revise it.

13:55.590 --> 13:56.870
If you have any questions, ask me anytime.

13:57.040 --> 13:57.440
Alright.

13:57.440 --> 13:58.910
Or you can ask my grandfather directly.

13:58.990 --> 13:59.600
Okay.

14:20.950 --> 14:21.640
Suye,

14:22.280 --> 14:23.400
are you free this weekend?

14:23.400 --> 14:24.080
No.

14:25.510 --> 14:26.590
I have clinic duty on Saturday.

14:27.320 --> 14:28.230
And on Sunday…

14:32.900 --> 14:35.070
There's a seminar on Sunday.

14:36.470 --> 14:37.630
Stop trying to fool me.

14:37.800 --> 14:38.470
It's blank.

14:38.470 --> 14:39.690
There's no seminar.

14:40.830 --> 14:41.870
You're free on Sunday.

14:42.110 --> 14:42.960
I've checked.

14:43.230 --> 14:44.510
Just get to the point.

14:50.750 --> 14:52.420
Help me with a blind date.

14:57.400 --> 14:58.320
Hey, Suye,

14:58.320 --> 14:59.040
don't leave!

14:59.040 --> 14:59.400
Suye.

15:01.370 --> 15:02.490
Suye.

15:03.680 --> 15:04.800
Help me out.

15:05.220 --> 15:06.490
You know

15:06.510 --> 15:07.240
that I like…

15:09.830 --> 15:11.160
I like Fang Kexin.

15:11.750 --> 15:12.710
So if I go on this blind date,

15:12.710 --> 15:14.320
I'll be wasting that girl's time.

15:14.850 --> 15:16.730
Then you shouldn't have agreed in the first place.

15:17.400 --> 15:19.790
My dad suddenly called and told me about it.

15:19.830 --> 15:20.440
I refused,

15:20.440 --> 15:21.110
and he scolded me for quite a while.

15:21.110 --> 15:22.230
How could I say no?

15:24.280 --> 15:25.110
Help me out.

15:25.560 --> 15:26.350
Look at me,

15:27.110 --> 15:28.590
I'm still a kid.

15:28.590 --> 15:29.590
How can I go on a blind date?

15:30.750 --> 15:31.400
You?

15:32.200 --> 15:33.920
You're 25.

15:34.040 --> 15:34.920
Still calling yourself a kid?

15:35.400 --> 15:36.280
Grow up.

15:37.350 --> 15:38.200
Besides,

15:38.560 --> 15:40.250
the girl wants to meet you.

15:40.400 --> 15:41.920
If I show up, that's straight-up deception.

15:42.520 --> 15:44.280
Aren't you better than me anyway?

15:45.100 --> 15:45.890
Look at you,

15:46.410 --> 15:48.580
you have a PhD and a good job.

15:49.160 --> 15:51.990
You became an attending physician in our department at just 30.

15:53.630 --> 15:54.400
And let's not forget—

15:55.230 --> 15:56.830
you're good-looking too.

15:56.830 --> 15:57.560
Enough.

15:58.110 --> 15:59.230
Stop flattering me.

15:59.830 --> 16:01.400
Have you finished all your work?

16:01.400 --> 16:02.680
Do you have nothing better to do?

16:04.540 --> 16:05.920
Please help me out.

16:06.710 --> 16:07.750
No.

16:07.750 --> 16:08.470
Please, please.

16:08.470 --> 16:09.440
I said no.

16:10.240 --> 16:11.040
Just this once.

16:15.230 --> 16:16.060
Just this once.

16:29.670 --> 16:30.830
Hello, do you have a reservation?

16:30.860 --> 16:32.370
Yes, my friend is at Table 3.

16:32.470 --> 16:33.680
Table 3 is over there.

16:33.680 --> 16:34.750
He's already waiting for you.

16:34.960 --> 16:35.960
Thank you.

17:24.810 --> 17:26.329
Miss Shen, right?

17:28.180 --> 17:29.270
Yes, that's me.

17:29.300 --> 17:30.000
Please, have a seat.

17:30.030 --> 17:31.270
Thank you.

17:39.260 --> 17:40.980
How about I introduce myself first?

17:41.160 --> 17:41.550
Okay.

17:41.710 --> 17:42.600
My name is Li Jie.

17:42.600 --> 17:44.360
I'm a graduate student at Jiang University Medical School.

17:45.120 --> 17:46.440
I'm Shen Xifan,

17:46.440 --> 17:49.230
currently working as the front office manager at Gunan Huating Hotel.

17:51.640 --> 17:53.510
So, here's the thing.

17:54.220 --> 17:56.460
I'm currently pursuing my master's degree

17:56.490 --> 17:59.490
and don't plan to focus on anything

17:59.510 --> 18:01.430
outside of my studies for now.

18:01.990 --> 18:03.790
So…

18:07.070 --> 18:08.200
Actually, same here.

18:08.200 --> 18:09.840
I'm planning to go abroad next year.

18:10.870 --> 18:13.030
-Nice to meet you.
-Nice to meet you.

18:16.220 --> 18:18.500
So you're also forced into this by your family?

18:19.550 --> 18:22.110
I spent two days thinking about how to reject you

18:22.130 --> 18:24.570
in a polite way without embarrassing you.

18:24.830 --> 18:26.200
I didn't expect it to be this easy.

18:26.510 --> 18:27.360
Yeah.

18:27.920 --> 18:29.550
So you spent two days at school thinking

18:29.550 --> 18:30.840
and came up with what you just said?

18:32.790 --> 18:33.470
I…

18:33.960 --> 18:35.310
I'm not great with words.

18:35.990 --> 18:38.030
And it's my first blind date, so I'm inexperienced.

18:38.840 --> 18:40.750
Actually, I don't have much experience either.

18:42.790 --> 18:45.270
So we'll just go back and tell our family

18:45.270 --> 18:47.640
that we don't like each other

18:47.640 --> 18:49.120
and won't see each other again.

18:51.510 --> 18:52.120
Works for me.

18:52.270 --> 18:53.380
Alright.

18:53.600 --> 18:54.200
Come on.

18:54.300 --> 18:54.780
Let's order.

18:54.800 --> 18:55.560
I'll do it, I'll do it.

18:55.590 --> 18:56.500
It's okay, it's okay.

18:57.200 --> 18:57.960
What do you want to eat

18:57.960 --> 18:59.120
or drink?

19:04.030 --> 19:05.230
Since you're studying TCM,

19:05.230 --> 19:06.430
what's your focus?

19:06.710 --> 19:08.030
I specialize in oncology.

19:08.270 --> 19:09.680
Sounds scary, huh?

19:09.920 --> 19:10.810
No, not at all.

19:10.900 --> 19:12.100
I've been seeing a TCM physician recently.

19:12.120 --> 19:13.310
He's also in oncology.

19:14.230 --> 19:15.120
What's his name?

19:15.120 --> 19:16.120
Maybe I know him.

19:18.600 --> 19:19.600
I can't remember.

19:21.270 --> 19:23.050
But he works at a clinic

19:23.080 --> 19:24.510
near my neighborhood.

19:24.510 --> 19:25.640
I went to him for insomnia.

19:25.920 --> 19:26.990
That's pretty common.

19:27.200 --> 19:28.160
The government encourages

19:28.160 --> 19:29.360
TCM physicians

19:29.360 --> 19:31.310
to work in clinics

19:31.310 --> 19:32.510
to serve the public.

19:32.510 --> 19:34.680
I'll probably do the same after I graduate.

19:34.680 --> 19:35.600
That sounds nice.

19:38.600 --> 19:40.070
I'm actually curious.

19:40.070 --> 19:41.440
What do you guys study

19:41.440 --> 19:42.990
in TCM?

19:43.160 --> 19:46.160
In undergraduate years, we learn theories.

19:46.550 --> 19:47.750
A lot of memorization,

19:47.750 --> 19:50.550
exams, and some hands-on practice too.

19:50.550 --> 19:51.600
They keep us pretty busy.

19:51.600 --> 19:52.640
As a grad student now,

19:52.640 --> 19:54.230
I'm interning at a hospital.

19:54.230 --> 19:55.400
I have a senior who guides me.

19:56.750 --> 19:59.120
So there are actually a lot of young TCM physicians.

19:59.120 --> 20:00.360
I thought they were all old men.

20:01.200 --> 20:02.790
My TCM physician is similar.

20:02.790 --> 20:04.070
He has a really funny way of speaking.

20:04.070 --> 20:06.070
I was really surprised when I first met him.

20:06.070 --> 20:09.030
Right? Many people think that we TCM physicians

20:09.030 --> 20:11.680
are all old and boring.

20:11.680 --> 20:13.160
But that's not true.

20:13.790 --> 20:14.600
Let me give you an example.

20:15.030 --> 20:17.230
Like the senior who's guiding me during my internship.

20:17.750 --> 20:18.840
Usually,

20:19.200 --> 20:20.600
he wears a white coat

20:20.880 --> 20:21.880
and glasses.

20:22.360 --> 20:24.310
Patients all think he's very gentle,

20:24.310 --> 20:26.550
stable, and reliable.

20:26.550 --> 20:27.790
But in reality,

20:27.790 --> 20:30.200
that's just the clothes doing the work.

20:30.200 --> 20:32.600
As a kid, he was so mischievous.

20:32.600 --> 20:35.440
He messed with me a lot and took me to climb trees

20:35.440 --> 20:36.810
and break windows and such.

20:36.900 --> 20:39.790
He even tricked me into eating a lot of raw medicinal herbs,

20:39.880 --> 20:42.870
claiming I should learn from Shennong and taste all the herbs.

20:43.120 --> 20:43.990
Mischievous, wasn't he?

20:45.400 --> 20:48.640
He hasn't changed much.

20:48.810 --> 20:50.330
He doesn't mess with me anymore,

20:50.670 --> 20:52.800
but the way he speaks…

20:54.440 --> 20:55.790
He's got a sharp tongue.

20:56.230 --> 20:57.640
Sometimes he roasts me so smoothly

20:57.640 --> 20:58.710
that I don't even realize it until later.

21:03.800 --> 21:07.120
Sounds just like my physician.

21:07.440 --> 21:08.030
Really?

21:09.030 --> 21:10.360
What's your physician like?

21:30.640 --> 21:31.400
You're back.

21:31.710 --> 21:32.710
Yes.

21:38.360 --> 21:39.360
How did the blind date go?

21:40.210 --> 21:41.380
It was okay.

21:41.440 --> 21:42.790
He's still in college.

21:42.790 --> 21:43.880
Just a kid.

21:44.400 --> 21:45.470
What do you mean?

21:45.470 --> 21:47.400
I mean, he's not interested in me.

21:47.750 --> 21:49.360
How can he not be interested?

21:49.360 --> 21:50.880
Well, I'm not interested in him either.

21:50.880 --> 21:52.230
We are not into each other.

21:53.030 --> 21:53.550
Mopping the floor?

21:54.270 --> 21:54.960
Dad,

21:54.960 --> 21:57.160
I want to have glutinous rice balls in osmanthus sweet soup tonight.

21:57.160 --> 21:58.470
Okay. You really don't like him?

21:58.470 --> 21:59.230
No.

21:59.230 --> 22:00.640
Dad, I'm hungry.

22:04.310 --> 22:07.160
If they aren't into each other, there's nothing we can do.

22:07.240 --> 22:09.090
She said he's just a kid.

22:09.650 --> 22:11.100
So she doesn't like younger guys.

22:12.440 --> 22:13.990
Does that mean she likes older ones?

22:14.470 --> 22:15.750
Older guys are sleazy.

22:15.750 --> 22:16.960
I wouldn't be interested in them either.

22:18.550 --> 22:19.680
I'm not that bad, am I?

22:37.750 --> 22:39.600
He was treated at another hospital before,

22:39.600 --> 22:40.750
and the results were pretty good.

22:40.950 --> 22:42.120
Why do you want to transfer hospitals?

22:44.200 --> 22:45.550
For his treatment,

22:45.550 --> 22:47.110
I've been working nonstop to make money.

22:47.750 --> 22:48.790
But I realized

22:48.790 --> 22:50.730
chemo was too painful for him.

22:50.790 --> 22:52.550
So I thought I'd try TCM.

22:53.160 --> 22:54.920
Mom, I'm not in pain.

22:55.880 --> 22:56.510
Good boy.

22:57.070 --> 22:58.400
I heard about it from others,

22:58.400 --> 22:59.680
so I came to check it out.

23:00.160 --> 23:00.950
Doctor,

23:01.200 --> 23:02.960
can TCM really treat leukemia?

23:03.550 --> 23:05.070
The main treatment for leukemia

23:05.070 --> 23:05.920
is chemotherapy.

23:06.360 --> 23:07.550
TCM treatments

23:07.550 --> 23:09.510
can reduce the side effects of chemo,

23:09.790 --> 23:11.190
making it less painful for the child

23:11.270 --> 23:12.400
and helping with a faster recovery.

23:13.960 --> 23:15.420
Do you feel uncomfortable anywhere?

23:17.470 --> 23:18.470
A bit of diarrhea?

23:20.030 --> 23:21.440
It feels like I could live in the bathroom.

23:22.640 --> 23:23.200
Alright.

23:26.310 --> 23:28.310
Based on his previous medical records and pulse diagnosis,

23:28.680 --> 23:31.310
this doesn't seem like chemo-induced enteritis.

23:31.990 --> 23:33.230
Now that it's autumn,

23:33.230 --> 23:35.550
it's likely viral-induced pediatric diarrhea.

23:35.840 --> 23:39.070
We may need to check the skin around his anus.

23:39.360 --> 23:41.270
If it's just pediatric diarrhea,

23:41.270 --> 23:43.200
applying some herbal medicine on the navel should be enough.

23:43.790 --> 23:45.360
But if not,

23:45.360 --> 23:46.680
further tests might be needed.

23:47.640 --> 23:48.550
Okay.

23:50.270 --> 23:52.780
Come on, let me check your anus.

23:52.870 --> 23:53.660
Take off your pants.

23:54.990 --> 23:56.070
No, Mom!

23:56.070 --> 23:58.440
If I don't eat, I won't have diarrhea. Is that okay?

23:58.440 --> 23:59.270
No.

23:59.840 --> 24:01.070
He's a doctor.

24:01.070 --> 24:02.030
Just let him take a quick look.

24:02.510 --> 24:02.840
Come on.

24:02.840 --> 24:03.360
Be good.

24:03.360 --> 24:04.120
No.

24:04.680 --> 24:06.750
If you're reluctant, you can let your mom check it for me.

24:07.600 --> 24:08.880
Better let the doctor do it.

24:08.880 --> 24:09.550
I don't know anything about it.

24:11.710 --> 24:13.510
Will the additional exams

24:13.990 --> 24:15.160
be expensive?

24:20.590 --> 24:22.940
Don't worry. This exam is free.

24:23.310 --> 24:24.980
But if you don't get properly examined,

24:25.010 --> 24:26.580
you might end up spending more money later.

24:29.270 --> 24:30.200
Alright then.

24:32.360 --> 24:33.640
Let's go. Be a good boy.

24:47.120 --> 24:48.550
Fortunately, it's just pediatric diarrhea.

24:48.550 --> 24:49.600
A herbal navel application

24:49.600 --> 24:50.460
will fix it quickly.

24:51.160 --> 24:52.200
It's raining outside today.

24:52.200 --> 24:52.990
Make sure to stay warm.

24:53.920 --> 24:55.200
He's not officially transferred yet.

24:55.200 --> 24:56.790
How do we go about the paperwork?

24:57.510 --> 24:58.680
I'll give you a form.

24:58.680 --> 25:00.750
After you go out, find the head nurse at the nurse station.

25:01.440 --> 25:02.640
As for the expenses…

25:02.790 --> 25:03.840
Doctor, don't worry.

25:03.840 --> 25:05.030
I'll pay whatever it takes,

25:05.030 --> 25:06.470
as long as my son gets better.

25:09.470 --> 25:10.550
What I mean is,

25:10.550 --> 25:11.880
if you're facing financial difficulties,

25:11.880 --> 25:13.790
I can help you get in touch with a charity fund

25:14.120 --> 25:15.360
to ease your burden a bit.

25:16.390 --> 25:17.500
Well...

25:17.520 --> 25:18.810
that's not necessary for now.

25:19.120 --> 25:20.640
I can still manage for a while.

25:21.960 --> 25:22.530
Alright.

25:22.920 --> 25:24.510
If you need anything, come to me anytime.

25:26.510 --> 25:27.360
You hear that?

25:27.360 --> 25:28.550
Be strong, okay?

25:29.640 --> 25:31.160
If I transfer to this hospital,

25:31.600 --> 25:33.320
will you be my attending doctor?

25:35.220 --> 25:37.070
You want me to be your attending doctor?

25:38.640 --> 25:39.600
Otherwise,

25:39.900 --> 25:42.070
another doctor will have to look at my butt.

25:42.200 --> 25:42.840
That's too embarrassing.

25:44.260 --> 25:46.110
You think we want to look at your butt?

25:46.840 --> 25:47.840
You little brat.

25:50.630 --> 25:51.320
Alright.

25:52.230 --> 25:52.990
Thank you, Doctor.

25:52.990 --> 25:53.620
The medical records.

26:06.260 --> 26:09.510
[Doctor's Lounge]

26:14.510 --> 26:15.680
Working hard, huh?

26:17.820 --> 26:20.210
You know, I was forced to go on a blind date yesterday,

26:20.550 --> 26:22.600
so I didn't have time to finish the bid proposal.

26:22.960 --> 26:24.270
Fang Kexin is going to scold me again.

26:25.920 --> 26:27.310
How was the blind date yesterday?

26:28.440 --> 26:29.310
Why?

26:30.640 --> 26:32.430
Maybe you can share some tips with me.

26:33.640 --> 26:35.360
Sorry to disappoint you.

26:35.360 --> 26:36.600
I have no tips to share.

26:37.470 --> 26:40.030
Both that girl and I were forced into it,

26:40.030 --> 26:42.120
so we just laid it all out

26:42.120 --> 26:43.360
and chatted casually.

26:44.440 --> 26:46.070
She's been seeing a TCM physician lately,

26:46.070 --> 26:47.030
so we talked about

26:47.030 --> 26:48.990
some TCM-related stuff

26:48.990 --> 26:50.360
and then went our separate ways.

26:52.160 --> 26:52.790
That's it?

26:53.710 --> 26:54.840
So boring.

26:54.840 --> 26:56.510
But that girl is quite interesting.

26:57.230 --> 26:59.470
She knows a lot about medicine after being sick for too long.

26:59.820 --> 27:01.300
She said she hated how bitter the decoction was,

27:01.960 --> 27:04.310
so she looked up all kinds of herbs online

27:04.710 --> 27:06.790
and even got her physician to change her prescription.

27:06.820 --> 27:08.030
Isn't that hilarious?

27:09.070 --> 27:10.710
I randomly asked her about a few herbs,

27:10.790 --> 27:12.630
and she actually got their properties

27:12.650 --> 27:14.510
and effects mostly right.

27:14.510 --> 27:15.550
Dr. He,

27:15.550 --> 27:18.470
can we remove goldthread from this formula?

27:18.470 --> 27:19.360
No.

27:19.360 --> 27:20.040
Alright.

27:20.270 --> 27:23.120
Then can we remove the processed gardenia?

27:24.280 --> 27:25.010
No.

27:26.890 --> 27:28.070
She's talented

27:28.400 --> 27:29.790
and so into TCM.

27:30.120 --> 27:32.160
It's a pity that she doesn't study it.

27:34.680 --> 27:35.920
Well,

27:36.750 --> 27:38.070
what does she do for a living?

27:38.600 --> 27:40.200
I think she's a hotel manager.

27:42.030 --> 27:42.840
Which hotel?

27:43.280 --> 27:45.560
The most famous resort hotel in our city.

27:45.790 --> 27:47.360
The one next to our herbal farm.

27:47.790 --> 27:48.550
What's it called again?

27:50.160 --> 27:51.040
Gunan Huating.

27:51.930 --> 27:59.360
♫Love love love love, is right in front of me♫

27:52.190 --> 27:53.030
Gunan Huating.

27:53.510 --> 27:54.360
No more chatting.

27:54.360 --> 27:55.270
I need to focus on writing this.

27:57.680 --> 27:58.550
Or I won't be able to finish it.

27:59.260 --> 28:01.150
You know, at our age,

28:00.040 --> 28:07.730
♫Ooh love, ooh love, I've seen your face♫

28:01.180 --> 28:03.030
our family loves to nag.

28:03.180 --> 28:04.450
Especially my mom.

28:04.470 --> 28:06.310
She nags nonstop.

28:06.310 --> 28:07.790
At home, she keeps saying,

28:07.790 --> 28:09.400
"You're already 27.

28:08.290 --> 28:15.550
♫Love love love love, is talking right at me♫

28:09.400 --> 28:10.510
Aren't you anxious?"

28:10.510 --> 28:11.440
What's there to be anxious about?

28:11.440 --> 28:12.640
Why should I be anxious?

28:12.640 --> 28:14.160
And it's not just her.

28:14.160 --> 28:15.200
My dad nags me too.

28:15.200 --> 28:17.030
It's like the two of them are doing a sketch.

28:15.860 --> 28:22.800
♫Loving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do♫

28:17.030 --> 28:17.920
It's totally...

28:18.390 --> 28:19.580
So it wasn't about getting married.

28:19.610 --> 28:20.660
They've already broken up.

28:20.780 --> 28:22.140
Why are you suddenly smiling?

28:23.460 --> 28:24.590
It's kind of scary.

28:23.570 --> 28:26.150
♫A gentle breeze begins to rise♫

28:27.120 --> 28:28.070
Nothing.

28:27.430 --> 28:31.980
♫You'll see a rainbow♫

28:29.370 --> 28:30.960
I'll teach you how to write it after work.

28:30.980 --> 28:32.180
You don't need to write it now.

28:32.010 --> 28:34.210
♫Hovering in mid-air♫

28:35.330 --> 28:37.930
♫This sweet dream♫

28:36.050 --> 28:37.000
I'm nice, aren't I?

28:39.680 --> 28:41.200
Why is it so scary?

28:39.930 --> 28:44.930
♫All our days are filled with♫

28:44.750 --> 28:46.230
I haven't done anything wrong, have I?

28:44.960 --> 28:48.540
♫Lololove and sunshine♫

28:48.720 --> 28:55.670
♫Loving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do♫

29:00.700 --> 29:01.650
Sorry.

29:01.790 --> 29:03.160
I suddenly remembered—

29:03.160 --> 29:04.790
Ms. Gu, who's staying in this room,

29:04.790 --> 29:06.520
loves wearing yellow in her casual outfits.

29:06.920 --> 29:08.360
How about we add some sunflowers

29:08.360 --> 29:09.990
to the floral arrangement?

29:10.230 --> 29:10.990
Of course.

29:10.990 --> 29:11.990
I'll redo it then.

29:11.990 --> 29:12.920
Thank you.

29:13.550 --> 29:15.200
Then this...

29:15.550 --> 29:16.470
Let me hold it for you.

29:16.470 --> 29:17.030
Alright.

29:17.510 --> 29:18.070
Thank you.

29:18.070 --> 29:18.750
Thank you for your hard work.

29:24.160 --> 29:24.840
By the way,

29:24.960 --> 29:26.810
I've finished setting up the rooms for the Goddess Day.

29:27.550 --> 29:29.440
Does the floral arrangement

29:30.270 --> 29:31.310
look good like this?

29:31.310 --> 29:32.160
Yeah.

29:33.230 --> 29:34.600
They have an evening flight.

29:34.600 --> 29:36.660
They'll arrive at the hotel around 10 p.m.

29:36.690 --> 29:38.820
So have them clean the rooms again before you leave work.

29:39.160 --> 29:40.160
Got it.

29:49.310 --> 29:50.640
Can I take

29:51.510 --> 29:53.030
some of these flowers?

29:53.840 --> 29:56.200
Sure, we won't need this many anyway.

29:56.470 --> 29:57.270
Thank you.

30:15.840 --> 30:16.680
Work hard.

30:23.920 --> 30:24.550
This is for you.

30:25.920 --> 30:26.440
This is for you.

30:26.440 --> 30:27.440
Mr. Chen,

30:27.440 --> 30:28.030
my champagne

30:28.030 --> 30:29.640
needs to be here by 6 p.m. sharp,

30:29.640 --> 30:31.160
or it'll be too late.

30:31.440 --> 30:32.200
Help me out.

30:32.200 --> 30:32.880
Make the arrangements.

30:32.880 --> 30:33.790
Thanks.

30:34.640 --> 30:35.790
What do you need?

30:35.790 --> 30:37.310
I'm busy. Make it quick.

30:38.550 --> 30:40.510
Looks like I came at a bad time.

30:55.200 --> 30:55.960
When you give someone flowers,

30:55.960 --> 30:57.200
you don't just give them one.

30:58.790 --> 31:00.980
It's an extra from the room decorations.

31:01.380 --> 31:02.900
Just take it.

31:11.990 --> 31:13.640
I overheard just now.

31:13.990 --> 31:15.270
Need my help?

31:17.070 --> 31:18.920
No. You can go.

31:19.740 --> 31:20.410
Alright.

31:23.160 --> 31:24.320
Go!

31:55.400 --> 31:55.990
Dr. He.

32:00.510 --> 32:01.340
Just got off work?

32:01.880 --> 32:03.120
We received a tour group today,

32:03.120 --> 32:04.310
so I worked overtime.

32:07.270 --> 32:09.200
Why do you look so happy?

32:10.140 --> 32:11.660
Something good happened?

32:14.860 --> 32:15.780
You could say that.

32:16.410 --> 32:18.340
I don't have much to congratulate you with,

32:19.120 --> 32:20.120
so take these flowers.

32:20.370 --> 32:22.040
Hope you can be happier.

32:22.360 --> 32:24.070
I didn't expect to get a bouquet when I was skateboarding.

32:24.640 --> 32:25.310
Thank you.

32:26.030 --> 32:27.710
You're welcome. Enjoy yourself.

32:27.710 --> 32:28.230
I'm heading home.

32:28.780 --> 32:29.300
Okay.

32:29.800 --> 32:30.640
Wait.

32:34.100 --> 32:35.300
I'm free next week.

32:35.320 --> 32:36.800
If you get off work early one day,

32:36.830 --> 32:37.700
come see me for moxibustion.

32:38.600 --> 32:40.310
I need more moxibustion?

32:42.790 --> 32:44.440
As a responsible doctor,

32:45.060 --> 32:46.900
I need to help you fully recover.

32:49.680 --> 32:51.680
Alright, I'll come to you when I have time.

32:53.510 --> 32:54.310
I'm really leaving.

32:55.200 --> 32:55.840
Okay.

32:56.160 --> 32:56.710
Bye-bye.

32:57.360 --> 32:58.030
Bye-bye.

33:04.860 --> 33:06.620
Why is he so happy?

33:51.160 --> 33:51.990
Hello, Manager Xu.

33:52.930 --> 33:53.730
Mom.

33:54.050 --> 33:55.130
Go ahead. What's it?

33:57.160 --> 33:58.070
Yes, I've eaten.

34:02.120 --> 34:02.710
Come back?

34:02.710 --> 34:04.460
At least wait until after the New Year, okay?

34:04.510 --> 34:06.030
After I get my year-end bonus.

34:08.360 --> 34:09.469
Whether it's a lot or a little,

34:09.469 --> 34:11.440
it's the money I worked hard to earn.

34:13.630 --> 34:15.190
You and Dad are still so young.

34:15.190 --> 34:17.130
You two can run it for a few more years.

34:17.920 --> 34:19.800
Why do you want me to take over so soon?

34:21.070 --> 34:21.840
Thank you.

34:24.550 --> 34:25.630
Mom, what are you thinking?

34:25.630 --> 34:26.989
They're all guests.

34:26.989 --> 34:28.469
I can't contact them privately.

34:29.500 --> 34:30.909
Alright, alright.

34:31.150 --> 34:32.790
I'll let you arrange blind dates for me when I'm back.

34:33.360 --> 34:34.030
I'm busy here.

34:34.030 --> 34:34.840
I have to go.

34:34.840 --> 34:35.719
Bye, Mom.

34:35.989 --> 34:36.800
Thank you, madam.

34:37.760 --> 34:38.550
You're welcome.

35:10.510 --> 35:11.470
Xiangya,

35:12.030 --> 35:13.240
it's past lunchtime already.

35:13.240 --> 35:14.630
Why are there still so many people?

35:14.970 --> 35:15.840
Haven't you noticed?

35:15.840 --> 35:17.030
They're all taking pictures,

35:17.260 --> 35:18.700
barely eating.

35:20.990 --> 35:22.070
Then what about my bubble tea?

35:23.630 --> 35:24.800
I don't think you can have it.

35:25.150 --> 35:26.320
I'll make you one later.

35:27.320 --> 35:28.280
Forget it.

35:28.470 --> 35:30.400
Dr. He doesn't let me drink bubble tea anyway.

35:31.760 --> 35:32.630
Handsome,

35:32.630 --> 35:34.070
let's take a photo together.

35:35.030 --> 35:35.990
Sorry,

35:35.990 --> 35:37.110
but the hotel has a rule.

35:37.110 --> 35:38.240
We're not allowed to take photos with guests.

35:38.240 --> 35:38.840
How about this?

35:38.840 --> 35:40.400
I'll take a group photo for you guys instead.

35:41.510 --> 35:42.720
Men know how to take pictures?

35:42.720 --> 35:43.150
I doubt that.

35:43.150 --> 35:44.440
As it happens,

35:44.440 --> 35:46.470
back in college, I took photography as an elective.

35:46.840 --> 35:48.070
Why don't you let me give it a try?

35:49.510 --> 35:50.510
Smile, smile.

35:50.510 --> 35:51.840
Be happy, be happy!

35:52.240 --> 35:53.070
Three.

35:53.070 --> 35:53.590
Two.

35:53.590 --> 35:54.150
One.

35:54.150 --> 35:55.920
Senior Lin fits right in

35:55.920 --> 35:58.590
at a place like this.

35:59.990 --> 36:01.360
Such a social butterfly.

36:06.550 --> 36:07.470
You all look good.

36:08.130 --> 36:09.290
Three, two, one.

36:12.150 --> 36:13.990
We just landed another big order.

36:13.270 --> 36:16.040
[Conference Room]

36:14.030 --> 36:14.990
In two weeks,

36:14.990 --> 36:16.960
a tour group from the neighboring province is coming.

36:16.960 --> 36:19.530
They're all well-off, elderly people,

36:19.760 --> 36:21.990
coming here for hot springs and physical therapy.

36:22.320 --> 36:23.070
What they want

36:23.070 --> 36:24.190
is relaxation and refreshment.

36:24.380 --> 36:25.500
They'll be staying for a week,

36:25.590 --> 36:27.370
with around 30 people in total.

36:27.720 --> 36:28.800
I've handed out the files.

36:28.800 --> 36:29.630
Take a look.

36:29.920 --> 36:30.880
Since they're all elderly people,

36:30.880 --> 36:32.550
most of them have health issues,

36:32.550 --> 36:34.240
so they've made special accommodation requests.

36:34.240 --> 36:35.400
Front Office, take note.

36:36.320 --> 36:37.720
And since this is a wellness trip,

36:37.720 --> 36:40.240
they've also made dietary requirements.

36:41.470 --> 36:43.470
The food needs to be light, nutritious,

36:43.470 --> 36:44.880
and also special.

36:45.670 --> 36:47.110
Isn't this the perfect chance for our Food & Beverage manager

36:47.110 --> 36:48.320
to showcase her abilities?

36:49.150 --> 36:51.400
Manager Lin, great job landing this order!

36:52.630 --> 36:53.510
You flatter me.

36:54.960 --> 36:55.630
Ah, right.

36:55.630 --> 36:57.440
Manager Lin, get in touch with the hospital.

36:57.440 --> 36:58.280
Since they're elderly people,

36:58.280 --> 36:59.990
medical needs might come up anytime.

36:59.990 --> 37:01.550
See if the hospital can provide some kind of collaboration.

37:01.990 --> 37:03.960
Also, arrange a training session for housekeeping staff

37:03.960 --> 37:05.440
on first aid for common elderly conditions.

37:05.670 --> 37:07.550
No problem. I'll reach out

37:07.550 --> 37:09.320
to the Municipal Third Hospital that's closest to us.

37:09.320 --> 37:11.240
Once I confirm the collaboration details, I'll update you.

37:11.960 --> 37:13.190
Alright, that's it.

37:13.190 --> 37:14.670
Everyone, go over the details…

37:15.510 --> 37:16.110
What's wrong?

37:16.300 --> 37:17.900
General Manager, I have a suggestion.

37:18.360 --> 37:19.720
Since this is a wellness trip

37:19.720 --> 37:21.110
for the elderly,

37:21.110 --> 37:21.960
I think we can incorporate

37:21.960 --> 37:23.720
some traditional Chinese medicine elements.

37:23.850 --> 37:24.600
Food & Beverage

37:24.630 --> 37:26.630
could offer medicinal cuisine and herbal tea.

37:26.800 --> 37:28.440
For example, licorice slices can be used to make tea.

37:28.730 --> 37:29.420
And Housekeeping

37:29.440 --> 37:31.800
could replace normal pillows with buckwheat pillows.

37:31.800 --> 37:32.430
For aromatherapy,

37:32.430 --> 37:34.760
we could use herbal scents.

37:36.030 --> 37:37.990
For a wellness trip,

37:38.630 --> 37:40.400
TCM would be a perfect fit.

37:40.400 --> 37:41.470
What do you all think?

37:41.790 --> 37:43.090
Sounds good. I think it works.

37:43.110 --> 37:44.190
I think it's doable.

37:44.720 --> 37:46.720
If we can do it well this time,

37:47.030 --> 37:48.670
we could turn the TCM wellness trip

37:48.670 --> 37:50.800
into a signature service of our hotel.

37:51.510 --> 37:52.630
I also think it's a great idea,

37:52.630 --> 37:54.840
but I've never had medicinal cuisine before,

37:54.840 --> 37:55.920
so I'm not very familiar with it.

37:55.920 --> 37:57.550
Wouldn't it be too bland?

37:58.240 --> 38:00.360
I've been seeing a TCM physician lately.

38:00.360 --> 38:02.670
He recommended a few medicinal dishes to me.

38:02.670 --> 38:04.510
The one that stuck with me the most was

38:04.510 --> 38:06.670
adding Chinese yam to the soup base of spicy hotpot.

38:06.670 --> 38:07.960
I think it's pretty interesting.

38:07.960 --> 38:09.800
But after all, medicinal cuisine contains medicinal ingredients,

38:09.800 --> 38:11.150
so we have to be careful

38:11.150 --> 38:12.590
and figure out

38:12.590 --> 38:15.240
the potential conflicts between different medicinal ingredients.

38:15.240 --> 38:16.320
And more importantly,

38:16.320 --> 38:17.240
these elderly guests

38:17.240 --> 38:18.590
already have health conditions.

38:18.590 --> 38:20.280
We need to make sure that the medicinal cuisine doesn't interfere

38:20.280 --> 38:22.070
with the medication they're already taking.

38:22.880 --> 38:24.960
Manager Shen, you sure know a lot about TCM now.

38:28.110 --> 38:28.960
Manager Xu,

38:28.960 --> 38:30.990
do you think this dining plan is feasible?

38:31.630 --> 38:33.550
I think it is.

38:33.990 --> 38:35.390
But since medicinal cuisine

38:35.410 --> 38:38.160
may involve conflicting herbal properties,

38:39.510 --> 38:43.070
we should probably have a TCM consultant, right?

38:43.850 --> 38:45.120
A consultant?

38:46.600 --> 38:47.460
Manager Shen,

38:47.510 --> 38:49.110
you've been seeing a TCM physician lately, right?

38:49.110 --> 38:50.240
Do you think your physician

38:50.240 --> 38:51.840
would be willing to be our consultant?

38:53.320 --> 38:55.000
I can ask him.

38:55.070 --> 38:57.550
He works at the municipal TCM hospital,

38:57.550 --> 38:59.590
so I think he's definitely qualified.

39:00.240 --> 39:01.150
No doubt about that.

39:01.340 --> 39:02.280
Alright, then it's settled.

39:02.280 --> 39:03.590
Manager Shen, Manager Xu,

39:03.590 --> 39:04.990
you two draft a proposal for the medicinal cuisine

39:04.990 --> 39:05.850
and herbal tea.

39:06.020 --> 39:06.920
If it gets approved,

39:06.920 --> 39:09.280
we'll allocate some funds as the consulting fee.

39:09.940 --> 39:10.540
Got it.

39:12.120 --> 39:13.250
Alright, that's it.

39:13.310 --> 39:14.790
Keep me updated if anything comes up.

39:15.360 --> 39:16.280
You may leave for dinner.

39:22.790 --> 39:24.270
No problem. I'm off.

39:24.760 --> 39:25.550
Bye-bye.

39:30.320 --> 39:31.510
What's going on?

39:32.190 --> 39:33.590
Didn't you say it's better to just be friends

39:33.590 --> 39:34.960
with that handsome TCM physician?

39:34.960 --> 39:36.030
Tell me the truth.

39:36.030 --> 39:37.030
Is there any progress?

39:37.030 --> 39:38.440
What progress?

39:38.440 --> 39:39.070
What are you saying?

39:39.070 --> 39:40.800
Then why are you out here helping him make money?

39:41.360 --> 39:42.320
Xiangya,

39:42.320 --> 39:44.360
the entire TCM wellness project

39:44.360 --> 39:45.840
is resting on your shoulders now.

39:45.840 --> 39:46.590
I've just

39:46.590 --> 39:48.880
offered you a great idea.

39:49.110 --> 39:49.840
If you keep this up,

39:49.840 --> 39:50.550
I won't contact my physician for you.

39:50.550 --> 39:51.880
You'll have to develop medicinal cuisine all by yourself.

39:51.880 --> 39:52.400
Fine, fine.

39:52.400 --> 39:53.590
I won't say that again.

39:53.590 --> 39:55.070
Hurry up and ask him for me.

39:55.360 --> 39:57.440
If he's willing to come, that's perfect.

39:57.440 --> 39:58.280
If not,

39:58.280 --> 39:59.630
I need to start looking for other options.

40:01.150 --> 40:04.470
Why don't we discuss it with Senior Lin?

40:05.840 --> 40:06.600
No need.

40:06.840 --> 40:07.760
He's busy coordinating

40:07.760 --> 40:10.320
with the medical team.

40:11.510 --> 40:12.670
Did you two have a fight?

40:12.670 --> 40:13.550
No.

40:14.670 --> 40:16.590
Just ask him for me.

40:16.590 --> 40:17.590
If he agrees,

40:17.590 --> 40:18.320
I need to include his profile

40:18.320 --> 40:19.670
in the presentation slides.

40:23.320 --> 40:24.390
[He Suye]

40:38.560 --> 40:39.520
Dr. He,

40:39.540 --> 40:41.270
are you free after work today?

40:44.720 --> 40:45.360
Yeah.

40:50.610 --> 40:51.920
I'll treat you to dinner

40:51.950 --> 40:53.720
and talk to you about something.

41:04.070 --> 41:04.690
Sure.

41:08.280 --> 41:09.280
See you tonight.

41:26.240 --> 41:27.150
See you tonight.

41:32.770 --> 41:33.400
I'm leaving.

41:42.990 --> 41:44.720
What is he planning?

41:45.290 --> 41:47.130
He's definitely up to no good.

41:53.590 --> 41:55.670
I'm meeting Dr. He for dinner tonight.

41:55.670 --> 41:57.740
I'll bring up our needs then.

41:57.800 --> 41:58.320
Okay.

42:00.280 --> 42:02.710
Did you upset Xiangya again?

42:03.150 --> 42:03.920
No.

42:04.080 --> 42:05.720
She always finds me annoying.

42:06.470 --> 42:08.360
Let me analyze this for you.

42:08.760 --> 42:09.510
I think

42:09.510 --> 42:10.800
you must have upset her.

42:10.820 --> 42:11.430
Look,

42:11.570 --> 42:13.700
you flirted with girls in her restaurant

42:13.760 --> 42:16.510
and even extended her restaurant's business hours.

42:20.320 --> 42:20.990
That?

42:21.990 --> 42:23.760
Wasn't I just helping her out?

42:24.130 --> 42:25.360
How would she know that?

42:25.360 --> 42:26.800
Just try to appease her later.

42:26.800 --> 42:27.670
I'm leaving, bye-bye.

42:27.670 --> 42:28.360
Bye-bye.

43:03.460 --> 43:10.900
♫Love love love love, is right in front of me♫

43:11.580 --> 43:19.270
♫Ooh love, ooh love, I've seen your face♫

43:15.360 --> 43:15.990
Ms. Wu.

43:17.360 --> 43:19.070
Hi, Dr. He.

43:19.830 --> 43:27.090
♫Love love love love, is talking right at me♫

43:19.840 --> 43:21.760
Ms. Wu, I'd like some angelica

43:21.760 --> 43:23.190
and lily bulbs.

43:23.470 --> 43:26.030
Oh, Dr. He, you've been feeling unwell lately?

43:26.030 --> 43:27.880
You keep coming for herbs.

43:27.390 --> 43:34.340
♫Loving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do♫

43:29.440 --> 43:31.030
Angelica and lily bulbs, right? Just a moment.

43:31.030 --> 43:31.670
Okay.
